Featuring 13,000 SF of contiguous space (up to 17,650 SF with Lower Level space) with a dedicated entrance. Adjacent to the lobby and coffee lounge.

This spec suite offers open seating and collaborative space, a large conference room, a kitchen/break room, and three private window offices.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located at the corner of SW 5th Avenue and SW Harvey Milk Street in the heart of downtown Portland, the J.K. Gill Building is steps away from mass transit, restaurants, cafes, hotels, and shopping destinations.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Bring your creativity, your brilliance, and your determination to create something new and unique in the heart of the city. The J.K. Gill Building draws inspiration from the architecture of the past to advance a common vision of the future, creating space for the people who will take us there.

From the ground floor up, dynamic teams are coming together in the J.K. Gill Building, establishing this as a place where great work is done.

Project highlights include a Peloton Studio & fitness center, spa grade showers, lockers & tenant lounge, secure bike parking, a ground floor coffee lounge, and operable windows. 

Renovation is underway, with core & shell delivering in August 2020!

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 100,000 SF of new-to-market, creative historic office space
